> Dear Benjamin, A little comment,
> I've just did a test ride to mlglade, and noticed
> that the header remark in xxx_callbacks.ml may
> confuse novice users as says " ... do not edit this
> file ..", precisely the file that has to be
> touched by the programer?.

Hello,

No the ...glade_callbacks.ml file IS autogenerated and should NOT be
edited.
The file you have to change is ..._glade_mail.ml : in this file you will
override the methods inherited from 
the class in the module ..._glade_callbacks


